/>\n鄧龍威打官司要幫<br />\n四個漁民被屈藏毒又要幫<br />\n<br />\n香港人被菲律賓搞到雞毛鴨血唔去幫<br />\n走去幫敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:19:04.000Z","msg":"你食屎啦 菲律賓幫手抗衡強國 <br />\n仲係美國係亞洲四大盟友<br />\n杜特爾特同trump fd到仆街<br />\n菲律賓人係香港第2大族羣<br />\n僅次華人<br />\n<br />\n連呢首歌頌對香港之愛ge歌都係菲律賓樂隊唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/a0fkB9rbfjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa0fkB9rbfjs&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN9ArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=7664570a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a0fkB9rbfjs</a><br />\n<br />\n邊忽係敵人呀<br />\n<br />\n康泰事件 只係菲律賓一個變態警察發癲 咁arm唔好彩搵著一個香港團脅持<br />\n並唔係針對香港人<br />\n我問當地人 好多都唔知有呢件事<br />\n國際間亦唔算好大肆報導<br />\n所以第日d人見到架旅遊巴係現場微笑影相係因為佢地以為係拍戲<br />\n<br />\n你睇下事後一周年菲律賓ge官方紀念活動仲多過香港<br />\n反而曾特狗只係識頒奶共勳章比出事ge團友同導遊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/210209_0da1ffbb7390e0d18208ea11ee2915b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F210209_0da1ffbb7390e0d18208ea11ee2915b8.png&h=89cdb711&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/210211_f093d8784bf97dc69af7af494d873e88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F210211_f093d8784bf97dc69af7af494d873e88.png&h=3124a3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/210213_2d20fdf8dab6d373b6e95b1dc4a40f7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F210213_2d20fdf8dab6d373b6e95b1dc4a40f7d.png&h=3c8136a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/210216_efba546934e12751f73cf7296c25b36b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F210216_efba546934e12751f73cf7296c25b36b.png&h=d5558ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於鄧龍威一事已經比人揭穿係大話連遍啦<br />\n佢自己係fb籌左百幾萬拎黎係監獄叫雞 收買獄卒 出街買靚野食<br />\n你問下作點解佢比人踢爆左講大話<br />\n隱瞞係事發前已經入境過菲律賓之後<br />\n係fb用買六合彩做比喻出左呢兩篇認死狗文章之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/211014_1ccbe6c6114dbd28c4517523dd1b17f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F211014_1ccbe6c6114dbd28c4517523dd1b17f1.png&h=034d8612&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/211017_d90b89a3f74455870a4d51841df437bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F211017_d90b89a3f74455870a4d51841df437bf.png&h=6eac14e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔夠兩日就delete左？<br />\n毒販威又屈菲律賓冇提供翻譯同拖延審訊<br />\n明明係有幫手搵翻譯 但比毒販威推晒<br />\n然後毒販威個代表律師不停係上庭前唔記得帶文件同無故缺席<br />\n先令到審訊一拖再拖<br />\n<br />\n仲有4個漁民呢單野擺明係阿朗翻版啦<br />\n佢地被人過左一棟就有<br />\n話就話係漁民 但原來係有個住南丫島ge中間人叫佢地去菲律賓拖走架船<br />\n而唔係去捉魚<br />\n每人幾萬蚊酬勞 去到唔洗即日開工<br />\n等order<br />\n一叫佢地上船就有警察拉人<br />\n而且佢地仲要冇簽合約<br />\n<br />\n比幾萬蚊你去旅行 仲要唔洗即日開工<br />\n傻都知有鬼啦<br />\n<br />\n你睇下部製毒機？<br />\n成個火爐咁大<br />\nD警察點抬上架船屈佢地呀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/11/211804_f2fd201124d5db4d59fc362c1b8a8a7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F11%2F211804_f2fd201124d5db4d59fc362c1b8a8a7d.png&h=68d46565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最鬼就係佢地比人拉之後<br />\n個蛇頭就失埋蹤<br />\n根本就係阿朗翻版<br />\n只係件事你菲律賓發生就扮可憐<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/34362/港人菲國製毒案-包食包玩利誘揸船回港-中介人神秘失蹤\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F34362%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8F%B2%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E6%AF%92%E6%A1%88-%E5%8C%85%E9%A3%9F%E5%8C%85%E7%8E%A9%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%98%E6%8F%B8%E8%88%B9%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN9ArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=7ac6a74e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/34362/港人菲國製毒案-包食包玩利誘揸船回港-中介人神秘失蹤</a>"},{"pid":"9cf98